        "name": "Agitate",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You send the target\u2019s mind and body into overdrive, forcing it to become restless and hyperactive. During the duration, the target must Stride, Fly, or Swim at least once each turn or take 2d8 mental damage at the end of its turn. The GM might decide to add additional move actions to the list for creatures that possess only a more unusual form of movement. The duration of this effect depends on the target\u2019s Will save.",
